## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sacubitril+valsartan (Entresto) 2014** = first FDA NEP + ARB combo HFrEF (PARADIGM-HF). enalapril 35+ year ACE-i 1L 가 ARNI 로 대체. 2021 HFpEF + HFmrEF 확장. 양자-VQE 의 NEP zinc-binding + ARB 결합 dual scaffold fit.
2. **dapagliflozin Farxiga 2020 + empagliflozin Jardiance 2021** = first FDA SGLT2 HFrEF (DAPA-HF + EMPEROR-Reduced). T2D 약 → HF 약 paradigm shift. 2021-2023 HFpEF EMPEROR-Preserved + DELIVER. mechanism 가 glucose-axis 가 아니라 cardio-renal direct (ketone? Na/H? lysosome?) — 미상.
3. **finerenone (Kerendia) 2021** = first non-steroidal MR antagonist. CKD-T2D 1L + 2024 HFpEF FINEARTS-HF positive. spironolactone TOPCAT marginal HFpEF 의 대체. 양자-VQE 의 MR pocket selectivity (steroidal vs non-steroidal scaffold) 직접 fit.
4. **vericiguat (Verquvo) 2021** = first FDA sGC stimulator HF VICTORIA — post-decompensation HFrEF. riociguat (PAH) 의 cardiac extension. heme-binding sGC pocket 가 양자-VQE 의 metalloprotein scaffold fit.
5. **mavacamten (Camzyos) 2022** = first FDA cardiac myosin inhibitor — obstructive HCM. β-MyHC allosteric. aficamten (Cytokinetics SEQUOIA-HCM) next-gen. 양자-VQE 의 myosin allosteric pocket fit.
6. **tafamidis (Vyndaqel) 2019 + acoramidis 2024** = ATTR-CM TTR tetramer stabilizer. 임상 의미 = 2019 이전 ATTR-CM untreated + symptomatic only → 2019+ disease-modifying. patisiran/vutrisiran TTR siRNA + eplontersen ASO 동시 paradigm. cross-cardiac_amyloidosis_specific.
7. **HFrEF 4-pillar GDMT (ARNI + β-blocker + MR antagonist + SGLT2i)** = 2021-2022 ESC + AHA/ACC guideline major shift. 2014 ARNI + 2020 SGLT2 추가 후 sequential titration → simultaneous 4-pillar early initiation.
8. **omecamtiv mecarbil GALACTIC-HF 2021** = cardiac myosin activator — HFrEF efficacy marginal + accelerated approval failed. 양자-VQE 의 failed-comparator value (negative result calibration).
9. **GLP-1 semaglutide STEP-HFpEF + tirzepatide SUMMIT 2024** = obesity + HFpEF cross-link. cardiometabolic axis 의 5번째 pillar 가능성. cross-obesity + metabolic.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HF 임상 의미 한정.

